In order to put to aws
-----------------
change database address
add mail credencials


CREATE A file tha keeps all the configuration:
	private static String bucketName     = "*** Provide bucket name ***";
	private static String keyName        = "*** Provide key ***";
	
AWS:

ssh to beanstalk:
ssh -i /home/and/Downloads/mykeypairnew.pem ec2-user@ec2-35-177-6-38.eu-west-2.compute.amazonaws.com


SCP:
scp -i /tmp/mykeypair.pem /tmp/mykeypair.pem ec2-user@ec2-35-178-143-206.eu-west-2.compute.amazonaws.com:/tmp/ 


create tar:
tar -czf workspace.tar.gz workspace

REMOVE DIR and its contents:
rm -rf dirname

